         Dots don't break root.  Only Dot's with an initial damage component (typically poison and disease) have a chance of breaking root.  Root has a variable duration (or mobs check resistance multiple times, I am not sure which) which leads to early breaks.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
